# Titan AI Portal v2.0 — Phase 2 Board Recognition

Phase 2 improves what the portal sees before Titan learns from a match.

## Added

- Stronger board-corner detection using multiple edge methods
- Board confidence and 10×10 grid confidence
- Automatic two-colour marble estimation
- Four-click confirmation when piece colours are detected
- Manual six-click fallback when confidence is low
- Lightweight camera stabilization
- Rejection of frames with hands, large motion or camera movement
- Low-confidence frame rejection
- Counter for covered or moving frames skipped

## Deploy

Upload the contents of this ZIP over the existing GitHub repository and commit. Railway redeploys automatically.

Keep the existing Railway variables:

```text
ADMIN_PASSWORD=your password
SESSION_SECRET=a long random secret
DATA_DIR=/data
MAX_UPLOAD_MB=500
SAMPLE_FPS=1.5
MAX_ANALYSIS_SECONDS=3600
```

Test with the same short video so you can compare Phase 1 and Phase 2.
